==English==

===Etymology===
From the belief that the [[mute swan]] sings before dying

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[swan]] [[song]]'''
# {{idiom}} a [[final]] [[performance]] or [[accomplishment]], especially one before [[retirement]]

===Synonyms===
*[[farewell performance]]
*[[last hurrah]]

